Requirements:
  - tcpdump + sudo access for network monitoring

Controls:
  'q': Quit the program
  arrows: scroll
  'a': Sort by age
  'A': Sort by average CPU usage
  'p': Sort by current CPU usage
  'P': Sort by PID
  't': Sort by cpu time usage
  'c': Sort by command line
  'U': Sort by user
  'r': Sort by bytes read
  'w': Sort by bytes written
  'u': Sort by bytes uploaded
  'd': Sort by bytes downloaded
  'n': Sort by priority
  's': Sort by status
  'm': Sort by RAM usage
  'y': Sort by TTY
  'i': Toggle between average and current bytes / second for read, write, upload, and download
